81
00:13:09,645 --> 00:13:18,075
V-Vegeta... he has... ridiculous
strength... You need to be prepared!

82
00:13:18,115 --> 00:13:19,445
I know.

83
00:14:10,505 --> 00:14:11,665
Vegeta!

84
00:14:14,675 --> 00:14:19,055
<i>Damn! What quick, heavy attacks these are!</i>

85
00:14:19,095 --> 00:14:23,055
<i>Kakarrot was fighting an opponent like this?!</i>

86
00:14:23,095 --> 00:14:28,475
How can this be? How can Vegeta
there be absolutely no match for him?

87
00:14:28,515 --> 00:14:30,025
This is bad!

88
00:14:40,535 --> 00:14:44,325
