89
00:14:44,365 --> 00:14:48,535
<i>I am the warrior Saiyan</i>
<i>people's prince, Vegeta-sama!</i>

90
00:15:10,475 --> 00:15:13,605
Bastard! This is having no effect at all!

91
00:15:13,645 --> 00:15:15,315
Vegeta-<i>san</i>!

92
00:15:37,675 --> 00:15:42,845
<i>I-I'm no match for him...</i>
<i>I'm simply no match for him...!</i>

93
00:15:52,605 --> 00:15:54,935
