94
00:16:01,655 --> 00:16:03,445
Kakarrot!

95
00:16:03,485 --> 00:16:07,285
Switch out, Vegeta. Majin Boo is strong.

96
00:16:07,325 --> 00:16:11,125
Stronger than anyone
else I've ever fought before!

97
00:16:12,665 --> 00:16:16,295
