98
00:16:16,335 --> 00:16:17,965
Kakarrot!

99
00:16:42,655 --> 00:16:47,365
<i>Kakarrot, you are one incredible guy...</i>

100
00:16:47,405 --> 00:16:50,955
<i>I was absolutely no match against Majin Boo.</i>

101
00:16:50,995 --> 00:16:54,495
<i>You're the only one who can fight with him.</i>

102
00:17:01,085 --> 00:17:05,345
<i>Kakarrot... the first time I met you</i>

103
00:17:05,385 --> 00:17:11,265
<i>was when I came to Earth as I was</i>
<i>conquering planets on the frontier.</i>

104
00:17:17,525 --> 00:17:19,525
So, you've shown up?

105
00:17:22,695 --> 00:17:26,655
What have you come
all this way for, Kakarrot?

106
00:17:26,695 --> 00:17:29,705
Don't tell me you've come to
say you're going to defeat me,

107
00:17:29,745 --> 00:17:32,455
or some other absurd joke, have you?

108
00:18:00,485 --> 00:18:03,365
<i>D-Damned if I'm about to</i>
<i>let something like this happen!</i>

109
00:18:03,405 --> 00:18:08,325
<i>I-I am the Saiyan prince! I am ultra-elite!</i>

110
00:18:10,245 --> 00:18:14,205
<i>There's no way I can be beaten</i>
<i>by a lower-class warrior like him!</i>

111
00:18:14,245 --> 00:18:17,745
<i>I am the greatest in the universe!</i>

112
00:18:20,085 --> 00:18:25,795
<i>Ever since then, I lived with the</i>
<i>goal of surpassing you, Kakarrot.</i>

113
00:18:30,515 --> 00:18:34,645
<i>It's said that the legendary Super Saiyan</i>
<i>can only appear in one out of a thousand...</i>

114
00:18:34,685 --> 00:18:36,975
<i>Even if the legend were true,</i>

115
00:18:37,015 --> 00:18:41,605
<i>the capacity to become a</i>
<i>Super Saiyan lies within me alone!</i>

116
00:18:41,645 --> 00:18:45,445
<i>There's no way that</i>
<i>lower-class warrior Kakarrot</i>

117
00:18:45,485 --> 00:18:47,945
<i>could become a legendary Super Saiyan!</i>

118
00:19:01,125 --> 00:19:05,425
<i>H-He's clearly surpassed</i>
<i>the Saiyan fighting level.</i>

119
00:19:05,465 --> 00:19:11,715
<i>I-Is the legend really true?</i>
<i>Is he... really a Super Saiyan?!</i>

120
00:19:20,145 --> 00:19:25,605
<i>From my own self-anger, suddenly</i>
<i>I was awakened... to being a Super Saiyan!</i>

121
00:19:25,645 --> 00:19:28,025
<i>I was trembling with the joy of it!</i>

122
00:19:28,065 --> 00:19:30,695
<i>Finally, finally, the time</i>
<i>when I had surpassed Kakarrot</i>

123
00:19:30,735 --> 00:19:34,075
<i>and returned as the Saiyan prince had come!</i>

124
00:19:47,425 --> 00:19:52,505
<i>However, in the end,</i>
<i>I was unable to surpass you.</i>

125
00:19:55,215 --> 00:20:01,395
<i>At first, I thought it was because</i>
<i>you had something to protect–</i>

126
00:20:01,435 --> 00:20:03,565
<i>that having a strong mind</i>
<i>towards defending something</i>

127
00:20:03,605 --> 00:20:07,565
<i>gave rise to some mysterious power...</i>

128
00:20:10,025 --> 00:20:15,995
<i>That certainly may be true, but if that were it,</i>
<i>then it would have been the same for me, now.</i>

129
00:20:16,035 --> 00:20:19,535
<i>It was to have my own way,</i>

130
00:20:19,575 --> 00:20:22,375
<i>it was for my own enjoyment,</i>
<i>it was to kill my enemies,</i>

131
00:20:22,415 --> 00:20:24,875
<i>and it was for my own</i>
<i>pride that I had fought...</i>

132
00:20:27,045 --> 00:20:33,555
<i>But, Kakarrot, you were different.</i>
<i>You don't fight in order to win,</i>

133
00:20:33,595 --> 00:20:36,055
<i>you fight in order to be certain you do not lose,</i>

134
00:20:36,095 --> 00:20:39,555
<i>and in order to keep reaching your limits.</i>

135
00:20:39,595 --> 00:20:43,435
<i>That's why you don't worry</i>
<i>about taking your opponent's life.</i>

136
00:20:45,565 --> 00:20:50,445
<i>In the end, you never did kill me.</i>

137
00:20:50,485 --> 00:20:56,735
<i>It's as if you knew that I would now</i>
<i>come to have the slightest bit of a heart.</i>

138
00:20:57,575 --> 00:21:03,375
<i>It's so maddening! That there should</i>
<i>be a Saiyan who loves to fight, yet is kind!</i>

139
00:21:03,415 --> 00:21:08,585
<i>Hang in there, Kakarrot!</i>
<i>You are Number One!</i>

140
00:21:30,445 --> 00:21:33,025
Please, anything but that!!

141
00:22:01,675 --> 00:22:04,395
A-Awesome <i>oni</i>!

142
00:22:15,485 --> 00:22:18,445
<i>Even the highly proud Vegeta</i>
<i>has at last taken off his hat!</i>

143
00:22:18,485 --> 00:22:22,285
<i>The battle between Son Goku</i>
<i>and Majin Boo continues.</i>

144
00:22:22,325 --> 00:22:26,575
<i>Goku, hang in there!</i>
<i>Protect the universe's tomorrows!</i>

145
00:22:32,165 --> 00:22:36,755
<i>Angel... Angel... Angel...</i>

146
00:22:38,505 --> 00:22:43,345
<i>Angel... Angel... Angel...</i>

147
00:22:47,555 --> 00:22:53,905
<i>Buried in time and distant memories,</i>

148
00:22:53,945 --> 00:22:59,985
<i>That's right, we were angels.</i>

149
00:23:00,025 --> 00:23:06,995
<i>From high in the sky we</i>
<i>scattered the seeds of love,</i>

150
00:23:07,035 --> 00:23:12,375
