<i>your courage swell up inside?</i>

153
00:23:25,385 --> 00:23:26,845
<i>Even now?</i>

154
00:23:26,885 --> 00:23:34,525
<i>To my friends, we may have lost</i>
<i>the wings from our backs, but still,</i>

155
00:23:34,565 --> 00:23:39,905
<i>There's some mysterious</i>
<i>power that remains with us.</i>

156
00:23:39,945 --> 00:23:46,365
<i>To my friends, let's embrace</i>
<i>the light and dare to dream,</i>

157
00:23:46,405 --> 00:23:56,415
<i>Look! I can see the rainbow in your eyes.</i>
<i>(Angel... Angel... Angel...)</i>

158
00:24:12,015 --> 00:24:13,935
<i>Heya! I'm Goku!</i>

159
00:24:13,975 --> 00:24:17,155
<i>Damn it, Boo's strength</i>
<i>ain't being diminished at all</i>

160
00:24:17,195 --> 00:24:18,775
<i>by these minor attacks.</i>

161
00:24:18,815 --> 00:24:21,905
<i>Kakarrot! I'll keep him</i>
<i>contained somehow for one minute!</i>

162
00:24:21,945 --> 00:24:25,495
