<i>to wipe him out in that time!</i>

163
00:24:25,535 --> 00:24:27,665
<i>Next time on Dragon Ball Z,</i>

164
00:24:27,705 --> 00:24:31,245
<i>"Pull Through, Vegeta!!</i>
<i>One Life-Threatening Minute."</i>

